translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「次はテメェもこんな姿に変える。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Next, I'll change you into a form like this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こっから先の対応は慎重にするんだなぁ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "From here on, handle things carefully, got it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （おかしい……どういうことなの……？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (This is strange... What does this mean...?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私の力はどんな者でも眠らせる……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: My power can put anyone to sleep...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （たとえ数千、数万の軍でも、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Even if it's thousands or tens of thousands of soldiers,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスのような最強の魔人でも……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Or a supreme demon like Kaiburis...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……待ちなさい、ケイブリス。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Wait, Kaiburis.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少しは考える時間をもらったって――」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let me have some time to think――"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「けっ！　時間稼ぎかぁ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Tch! Trying to buy time, huh!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やることがみみっちいなぁ！　ええ！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Your actions are so petty! What!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おかしいって思わなかったか！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Didn't you think it was strange!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、既に思ってるんだろう！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, you were already thinking so, weren't you!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんでこいつは寝ないんだろう……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Why doesn't this guy fall asleep...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ってなぁ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's what I mean!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「グヘヘ、言ったことなかったよなぁ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ghehe, I never told you this before..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぐぁはぁはぁはぁはぁはぁはぁはぁ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gwahahahahahahaha!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様はスーパーウルトラ究極の不眠症なのよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I am the super ultra ultimate insomniac!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんたって、もう三千年も寝てねぇんだ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "After all, I haven't slept in three thousand years!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 眠らせてもらえんなら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If I can't be put to sleep,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 逆に寝させて欲しいくらいだぜぇぇ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'd rather want to be let to sleep instead!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ストロガノフが言うには、あまりに眠らなすぎて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Stroganoff says that because I don't sleep too much,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 体が睡眠しないよう進化したんじゃないかーとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: My body may have evolved to avoid sleep— or something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それこそ眠くなるようなこと抜かしてたが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He was spouting stuff like that would make me sleepy... but—"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「大事なのはただ一つ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The only important thing is one!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺様がテメェの天敵だってこと！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I am your natural enemy!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その一点だけだぜぇぇぇぇ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's the one and only thing!"
"What..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「オラオラオラ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ora ora ora!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか出来るものならしてみやがれ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you can do something, try it!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「オラオラオラオラオラァァァァァ！！！！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ora ora ora ora oraaaaa!!!!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリスの巨大な拳が激突し、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kaiburis's gigantic fist struck violently,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ワーグの小柄な体が枯れ葉のように吹き飛ばされ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Warg's small body was blown away like a dry leaf,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 樹木に叩きつけられた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and slammed against a tree.
"Ugh, ah, ha...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 肺の中にあった全部の酸素を吐き出して、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He expelled all the oxygen from his lungs,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ワーグが悶える。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Warg writhed in pain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺様は優しいから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm kind, so,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: スーパー手加減してやったが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I held back super hard, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘヘヘ、テメェの体じゃ効くだろう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, that should affect your body."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふわぁ〜……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Fuwaa~... (yawn)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 退屈すぎて、あくびが出ちまうぜぇ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This is so boring, it's making me yawn.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なぁぁぁんちゃってなー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just kidding—"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「んっ、ぐっ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Nn, gu..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: んぁぁ……なんか頭がボーッとすんなぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Naaah... my head feels all foggy...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それによ、こう……うとうとーっと……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And, like... drifting off to sleep...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あれ？　俺様、まさか眠い？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh? Am I... sleepy?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ヘッ！　まあそれでもいいぜえ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh! Well, that's fine too!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その前にテメェを百回は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before that, I can tear you apart a hundred times over,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 八つ裂きにできるんだからよぉ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so bring it on!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあさあ、そろそろ決めてもらおうか！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Come on, come on, it's time to decide!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様の味方になるのか！　敵になるのか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Will you be my ally or my enemy!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「敵になるなら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If you choose to be my enemy,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今ここで肉片になるだけだがなぁぁあ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you'll just end up as meat chunks right here!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「っ、ふっ、ぅう……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh, huh, ugh..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとかワーグが立ち上がる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, Warg managed to stand up.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目の前にいるケイブリスの巨体は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The giant figure of Kaiburis before him,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Stroganoff says that because I don't sleep too much,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He was spouting stuff like that would make me sleepy... but—"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「オラオラオラオラオラァァァァァ！！！！」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and slammed against a tree.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Warg writhed in pain.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh! Well, that's fine too!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before that, I can tear you apart a hundred times over,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so bring it on!"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Come on, come on, it's time to decide!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you'll just end up as meat chunks right here!"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh, huh, ugh..."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, Warg managed to stand up.
